---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Primary Care Doctor in Dallas–Fort Worth | AymanCare"
  description="Annual physicals, preventive screenings and chronic care management from a primary care team at four DFW locations. Medicare and Tricare accepted."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Primary Care\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/primary-care/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Primary Care</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Most requested service</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><em>Primary</em><br>care.</h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">A long-term partner in your family's health. Annual physicals, preventive screenings, and the steady, considered care that keeps small concerns from becoming big ones.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">All ages</span><span class="pill pill-accent">Medicare & Tricare</span><span class="pill">Same-day appointments</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book this visit →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/primary-care-clinic.jpg" alt="Primary Care">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Service details</div>
        <h3>What's <em>included</em></h3>
        <ul><li>Annual physical exams</li><li>Preventive screenings</li><li>Chronic disease management</li><li>Medication management</li><li>Referrals & coordination</li><li>Lab work & diagnostics</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Ready to book?</div>
        <h3>Same-day <em>appointments</em> available.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Call or book online — walk-ins welcome at every location.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2>Dedicated primary care in <em>Dallas.</em></h2><p>A primary care provider is a healthcare professional that delivers ongoing healthcare services. Aside from diagnosing and treating acute and chronic illnesses, a primary care physician is often the first point of contact when pursuing healthcare options — and a steady partner through every stage of life.</p><h2>What makes AymanCare <em>different.</em></h2><p>At AymanCare, your visits with Dr. Khan aren't rushed. We believe great care requires time — time to listen, time to ask questions, time to coordinate the right referrals. Our team uses data and technology to coordinate services so that when you come back, we already know you.</p><blockquote>"The best primary care visit is the one that leaves you feeling heard, clear on next steps, and confident in who's walking the road with you."</blockquote><h2>Who we <em>see.</em></h2><p>We see patients of all ages — from pediatric check-ups to senior wellness exams, from newborn visits to Medicare-covered preventive care. Whether it's your first visit or your fiftieth, the goal is the same: the best possible health outcome for the person in front of us.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col"><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">ABFM</div>
      <h4>Board-certified</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">10+</div>
      <h4>Years serving DFW</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">98%</div>
      <h4>Patient satisfaction</h4>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<section class="related-services">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
        <div>
          <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid"><a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Walk-In</em> Urgent</h4>
          <p>Same-day care for acute illness, injury, and COVID testing.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/pediatric-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Pediatric</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Child-centered care from newborn to teen.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/flu-treatment/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Flu</em> Symptoms</h4>
          <p>Rapid flu diagnosis and treatment.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a></div>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Ready when you are</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's take care<br>of <em>you.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Book online in under a minute, or walk into any of our four Dallas-area locations today.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
